cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on automatic art analysis and classification of Buddha statues using deep learning features. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with a dataset of images of Buddha statues. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper proposes a method for automatically recovering the proportions of Buddha statues using deep learning. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses deep learning features for classification tasks. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with the identification and classification of displaced art pieces.
